element.name: My name is... by the incachibles, Unknown Cache (2/1.5)
element.description: This is my very first hide so I hope you will like it.The cache is hidden in a park where I've been walking my dog every now and then.Its close to where I live as well. The coordinates above will take you to one of several entrances of the park,for the actual coordinates you will need to look very close at my account name.Park is accessible 24/7/365 and there is loads of free parking everywhere.Bring your own pen as the cache is too small to hold one. Below is the key to the real coordinates.
element.long-description:
There will be 15 steps and each step will give you one digit of the real coordinates.
Letters from A to G will stand for numbers from the first coordinate,A is first digit,B second ,C third etc.. Letters from H to O will stand for numbers from the second coordinate.H is first,I second etc...
Look at my name -The Incachibles-
A - number of letters in second word minus 6 B - number of letters in first word C - how many letters "i" are there in my name D - number of letters "c" plus letters "i" in my name E - number of letters in first word F - number of letters in the second word minus 2 G - how many caches have I hidden prior to this one using this account ...
H - number of letters "z" in my name I - number of digits in my name J - number of letters in the first word multiplied by 2 K - number of letters "t" in my name L - number of words in my name M - the answer to question C(third) multiplied by 2 N - the answer to question A plus answer to question B minus 7 O - number of letters in the first word multiplied by 2 minus 1
Good luck with this one!
Additional Waypoints AA1MX5B - entrance to park N 53째 24.360 W 006째 12.725
